    },
    {
      "text": "Bow Tie Electric Solutions is WONDERFUL! FAST, FRIENDLY and Efficient. We are so impressed with Billy and David's dedicated work ethic. They completed a job another electrician could not do- did not even attempt to do. We are so pleased and will use their service, always!!",
